{"tid":1554733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 產品設計文宣正式上線啦","createTime":"2019-09-09T05:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T04:00:43.000Z","uid":61160,"like":56,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"10309122181bd169b049ce112d4606f4a5b58dbf","tid":1554733,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我地係幾伙設計系畢業生既小團隊，當中亦有喺今次運動中走得比較前既手足。<br />\n係大約一星期前我地因為自己既興趣做左一隻小勇武，亦都放左係post左係fb。因為好想好想將香港人嘅勇氣、團結同堅持記錄落嚟，亦都紀念同感謝各位兄弟姊妹，特別係走得較前嘅手足嘅付岀。結果反應出乎我地想像，好多人提議我地義賣但其實3d print成本太高我地真係冇諗住賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyexLqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyexLqs.jpg&h=1854554d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1OeRgxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1OeRgxb.jpg&h=8337f37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSxzeiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSxzeiS.jpg&h=f8b5e186&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到見到有post話商台曾經聯絡到台灣既義士連生活費都成問題，由個陣開始我地討論不如量產再將所以收益扣除成本捐哂啲錢比台灣個邊同星火。原本亦諗過捐比612個係佢地批錢好似好少，有人聯絡過我地話好似得個萬幾蚊?!<br />\n<br />\n所以我地決定係kickstarter眾籌。其實係商台個個訪問出街之後我地都立即有呢個打算，係一兩日之後已經打緊稿同係kickstarter申請緊，亦都諗住kickstarter成功審批之後先同大家講。但係我見到呢幾日有幾個post話出面有一個基金係比前線勇武，結果大家可能會質疑佢個可信性。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地想係呢到公開我地campaign個preview等大家比下意見，例如金額上多少既問題，做法點樣比較好，而設計上就唔會點改咖啦。kickstarter審批大約9月12號完成，係呢到公開我地既做法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wearehongkong377/hong-kong-warrior-of-liberty?ref=cy9j4n&amp;token=80270cb3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fwearehongkong377%2Fhong-kong-warrior-of-liberty%3Fref%3Dcy9j4n%26token%3D80270cb3&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=dd44f5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wearehongkong377/hong-kong-warrior-of-liberty?ref=cy9j4n&amp;token=80270cb3</a><br />\n<br />\n大家會可能質疑我地本人既誠信，我地其實係個人fb已經post左咖啦 ( 知道既巴打勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），我相信如果真係利用呢件事去呃錢既話我地既朋友都唔會放過我地。<br />\n<br />\n當眾籌後會馬上扣除成本將所有錢捐比星火同台灣義士。如果到最後我地真係冇方法搵到佢地，我地會將啲錢捐哂去星火。當然我地最最最希望既係幫到台灣既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n另外其實我地暫時亦都有遇到以下問題既：<br />\n<br />\n我地其實有嘗試過唔同channel去搵台灣個邊啲義士，但係暫時我地都未搵到，希望各連登仔可以幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n祝各位武運昌隆，五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"1eea65bc9eb3e196127ed31bdb751110c94dc893","tid":1554733,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8f873ad89bf38ae945dc4e7407a3a6f6768d5432","tid":1554733,"uid":317299,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b7313bdff7704cd9245cee4dec1ae3196f205dc","tid":1554733,"uid":41050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd87baa0b77c3f18ba2f8e5640a48c583976e1a","tid":1554733,"uid":61160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"自推x10"},{"pid":"61bcbbcf015148a53594d780e8f6b67d09bb8fb9","tid":1554733,"uid":61160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"大家可以比下意見咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左設計上真係唔會點改<br />\n另外想問下大家聯絡台灣義士既方法，唔想錢到手要keep住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7a746d2e2755053d4d33e02de1dfad92321447","tid":1554733,"uid":67755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"支持 但請問係唔係搵大陸廠整？"},{"pid":"553902fc55756b254cf223842853494ba4b1d1b6","tid":1554733,"uid":277483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"出左必買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cf5d7f57764f75e47dba5d3d5b8e0fd73e387c","tid":1554733,"uid":285915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"最近好似好多人話英文嘅文宣唔夠，又話鬼佬想睇到啲翻譯左嘅新聞。其實又班香港人已經做緊架啦。<br />\n（跪求幫推） 其實香港有班人好努力做翻譯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545086</a><br />\n我哋網站叫<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e2af3872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com</a>，我哋每日都會將香港嘅新聞翻譯再放上fb，tg，同埋twitter。小弟p牌冇得推po，唯有靠大家幫手推到外國人都知香港發生咩事。<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FCommunity-Organization%2FBeWater-HK-2406628919558580&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=a87a2ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhkg%2F%3Figshid%3Dwe1lffxlqh9f&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=76ca9611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg\" data-sr-url